data.description: Welcome to this meticulously owned and tastefully updated home in the Holmesburg section of NE Philadelphia. As you arrive to the property you will be greeted with a beautiful patio perfect for entertaining friends and family. Enter into a spacious living room area that leads into the formal dining room adjacent from an open concept kitchen. Property is equipped with hardwood flooring throughout and ceramic tiling in the kitchen. On the second floor you will find 3 generously sized bedrooms and an updated bathroom with beautiful ceramic tiling throughout. Finished basement with a full 3-piece bathroom.  Property features a 1 car garage, a good sized driveway with a huge shed perfect for all of your storage needs, and an updated laundry room. Open House scheduled for Sunday, September 17th.
